data.description: This beautifully constructed and maintained home is right across the street from West Salem High School.  You'll live large in this quiet & open concept home w/ 9ft ceilings & primary suite on main level.  Backyard boasts astro-turf, a custom gas-fed fire pit, retaining wall, pavers and separate fenced area for kids or dogs.  Front yard irrigation w/ 2 zoned drip & sprinklers & ability to extend. The interior is hardwired for all of your streaming and internet needs.
